* text=auto eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf
gradlew text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.keystore binary

# Bench-flavor fixtures — bundled media for the :app `bench` flavor.
# Mark as binary so diffs do not try to render them. If the total
# bundled media under app/src/bench/assets/ exceeds ~20 MB, migrate
# these extensions to Git LFS (track them with `git lfs track "*.mp4"`
# etc. and update this file accordingly).
*.mp4 binary
*.m4v binary
*.mov binary
*.m3u8 binary
*.ts binary
*.aac binary
